BBNaija star, Nina Ivy has been gifted a brand new Range Rover by her husband to begin the new month. The reality TV show star made this known in a recent social media post she made on her verified Instagram page. Sharing a photo and a video, she wrote; “It’s good when you follow your dreams
And even better when you drive your dreams … Thanks Hubby for my new baby #RangeRover #mybigdaddy #mybabygotmeababy #waytooblessed” View this post on Instagram A post shared by Nina ivy A (@nina_ivy_)